Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:24.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,能够治愈  诅咒  或是守护的符号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Symbols that cure or curse or protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,这都是迷信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all superstition,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是大家有信仰自由的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but people can believe what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是个自由的国度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a free country.
