Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是美洲的早期移民吃火鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that early American settlers feasted on turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实呢  鸭子还有可能  甚至是天鹅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, duck, maybe. Swan, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,但绝对地  大量地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But most certainly, bountifully,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是食用生蚝  -我爸爸宁愿我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- on oysters. - My dad would rather us be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,尊重史实而非开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}historically accurate than happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特欣赏历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert appreciates history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,他也许是我认识的最聪慧的学生之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He may be one of the sharpest students I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我告诉过他  原始智力只能让你到达一定程度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I've told him that raw intellect can only get you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:39.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,而另外一方面  生蚝呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raw oysters, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,就完全不同了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a very different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,实际上的确是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indeed, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:46.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我没注意时间  -笛卡尔的确会让你这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I lost track of time. - Well, Descartes will do that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我女儿正在写一篇关于《论灵魂的激情》的论文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My daughter is doing a thesis on Passions of the Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,一开始我还以为是一本浪漫小说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I originally thought it was a romance novel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我错了  并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I was wrong. It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,但它的确把胡言乱语浪漫化了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it does romanticize nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你读过他的著作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever read him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我尝试过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,天才数学家  当他讲到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Genius mathematician. He lost me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,松果体是通往灵魂的门户时我就放弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he said the pineal gland was the gateway to the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能反驳这种说法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you disprove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要吗  以我来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I need to? A-As far as I can tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对解剖学的理解还非常原始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he had a prehistoric understanding of anatomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,可他假定出了精神生理的定律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet he posited psychophysiological laws
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:20.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,-直到今天仍有意义  -精神生理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- that are still relevant today. - Psychophysiological.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得提到过你对伪科学很感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter mentioned you're into the pseudosciences.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:24.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,"非凡的头脑会被非凡的事情所吸引"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"A credible mind drawn to incredible things"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the way I put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我提议我们换个话题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suggest we change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,扎克里  不如你和我们说说你的行程吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zachary, why don't you tell us about your itinerary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我儿子要去中东\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, my son is going to the Middle East
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,围攻亚喀巴那里的沙滩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to lay siege to the beaches of Aqaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实只是想要离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just to get away from here, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I-I just mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,总是这个样子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is it always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,互相辩论  交流想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, debating, exchanging ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕那些想法不算...特别理性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even if they aren't... credibly rational?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What... I-I just mean, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们非常幸运...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're all very lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,能有这个家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次你真是中了头彩了  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really hit the jackpot with this one, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:11.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,每一年  所罗门教授接纳一个游子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each year, professor Solomon takes in a stray
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:14.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,来过感恩节  作为某种慈善活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for Thanksgiving as some sort of a charitable exercise,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,可实际上  他就是要找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, really, he's just looking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,一位新的听众来奉承他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for a new audience to fawn over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,他没有意识到的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What he doesn't realize is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你和我们一样根本不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you don't really care any more than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他确实在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们能留下他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can we keep him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:39.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他赢得了邀请  可以随时来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he's earned an open invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,等主管和你谈过后通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, let me know when you hear from the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时  我们搜查整座大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, we sweep the building
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,-将其封锁  -收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- and keep it locked down. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是这里的负责人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you in charge here or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  暂时是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Um, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,暂时  暂时是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now? What does that-what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,等我一下  行吗  女士  你不能留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give me a sec, okay? Ma'am, you can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,-这是犯罪现场  -那么你也许不应该\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is a crime scene. - Maybe you shouldn't let
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,让一群游客把这里的照片发到推特上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a bunch of tourists tweet photos of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -只是我的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Excuse me? - Just a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我应该把这个拿出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}佐藤井上  中情局特工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐藤井上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inoue Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,中情局  我以为联调局负责绑架案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CIA? I-I thought the Bureau handled kidnappings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  有时候是  看情况吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They do. Sometimes. It depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再说什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't really say anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说一下  那两位是和我一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those two are with me, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要全部权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll need full access.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这只手可能属于彼得·所罗门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I understand this hand may have belonged to Peter Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  你认识他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,-听说过  -这是罗伯特·兰登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of him. - Ah, well, this is Robert Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是所罗门先生的同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a coworker of Mr. Solomon's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,-嫌疑犯给他打过电话  两次  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The suspect called him. Twice. - Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不是同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we-we're not coworkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在哈佛大学教书  符号学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I teach at Harvard. Symbology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得是我的导师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter was my mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上  我接到了他助理的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This morning, I got a call from his assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少  我当时以为是他的助理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Least, thought it was his assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说  彼得想让我过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said that Peter wanted me to come down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,在国会大厦的晚宴上演讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}speak at the Capitol at this gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道彼得不太会考虑别人的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter's not known for his consideration of other people's time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以当时我并没觉得很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it didn't seem out of the ordinary to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-要立马坐飞机...  -罗伯特  深呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- to get on a plane... - Robert. Take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个人说过他的目的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did this person say what he wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不会理解的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It won't make sense to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是先告诉我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:02.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说他正在寻找一个古老的入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he's looking for an ancient portal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,就掩埋在这座城市里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}buried within the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想让我找到并打开它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants me to locate - and unlock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,这对你来说有什么含义吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that means something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:10.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我直到看到那个才明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It didn't until I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,在另外三根手指上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the other three fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们会发现更多的文身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect you'll find more tattoos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,太阳  灯笼  和钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A sun, a lantern and a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,他仿造了一只神秘之手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's replicated the Hand of the Mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:30.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个贯穿历史的符号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an icon you see throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,是炼金术师和秘术家的信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The alchemists, the cabalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一封邀请函  邀请你越过神秘的大门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an invitation to seek a body of ancient knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,去寻找神秘的知识体系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beyond a mystical gateway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:39.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,疑犯在之前将手吊在石膏里  装成自己的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the suspect walked through security earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,正大光明地走过了安检\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with his hand in a sling like it was his.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且我觉得他还做了伪装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he was wearing makeup, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,-涂了遮瑕膏  -你的眼力很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Concealer. - You got a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:52.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,看看警官能不能调出一些疑犯的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if the sergeant can pull some security stills of the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得手上的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ring on Peter's hand--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,三十三级共济会会员戒  据我所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}33rd-degree Mason. From what I remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,有了这个就能接触到一些古老的知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that comes with some ancient knowledge of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论人们怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Despite what some people think,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,共济会本质上就是个社交俱乐部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Masons are essentially a social club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这仍然有可能是他被盯上的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still, it could explain why he was targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个家伙认为彼得了解入口的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this guy thought Peter knew about the portal thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  他会非常失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he would've been sorely disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得知道  这家伙想要的东西不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter knows that what this guy is after doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得有个女儿  对吗  你和她是什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has a daughter, right? What's your relationship with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们是朋友  -我们得确保她的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Uh, we're friends. - We need to make sure she's secure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也需要做个基因检测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we'll need a DNA reference
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,来确认那确实是她父亲的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to confirm that's actually her father's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来吧  我先给她打个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, let me do it. Let me-let me call her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳  有情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine. Something's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲  他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's your dad. He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,他被带走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, um, I don't know exactly what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们会把他救回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we're gonna get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们离开圆形大厅了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have they left the Rotunda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不能待在这里  公园关门了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you can't be in here, man. Park's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我没注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, I didn't realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要挂了  妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Ma, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,里奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来会穿那种衣服吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, does it look like I'd wear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:22.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以之前在国会大厦的人不是你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that wasn't you by the Capitol earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  他们在审核我的最高法院职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah. They were vetting me for the Supreme Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:27.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱  身份证拿出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, very cute. Let's see some ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想惹麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, I don't... I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,检查一下身份证  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just want to see some ID, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,别  住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,解放  自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Liberty. Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,合众为一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}E pluribus unum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,十三  十三  十三个州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}13. 13. 13 states.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,当地警方在运河路附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Local PD found Solomon's car
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个停车场发现了所罗门的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in a lot off of Canal Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有监控  没有目击者  没有打斗痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No cameras. No witnesses. No signs of struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要是知道我们对此案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, it would be helpful if I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,真正的兴趣在哪就更好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what our actual interest in this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,解放  自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Liberty. Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,十三位少女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}13 maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:00.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,"彼得将会给你指路"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Peter will point the way."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在电话里说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said that on the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们上方的壁画是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fresco above us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁米迪所画的《华盛顿的神化》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is Brumidi's Apotheosis of Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:17.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,源于希腊语  "成为上帝"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the Greek "Apo," To become, and "Theos," God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,那里  正中间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There, in the central panel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:24.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,乔治·华盛顿乘着云朵从凡人中飞升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George Washington is ascending on a cloud above the mortals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的蜕变时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His moment of transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:30.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想这个家伙也在告诉我们他想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think this guy is telling us what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,神化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apotheosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,他以为接触了这些古老知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To become a god. And he thinks he can do that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,就能让他成为上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by accessing this ancient knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,据说其中存放着能够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was said to hold the keys to unlocking abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,解锁人脑中潜藏能力的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that lay dormant in the human mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是跟着他的思路走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm-I'm playing catch-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,可赎金竟然是超能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but th-the ransom is superpowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,他正在做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything he's doing is-is in accordance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,都与古老的条约一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with ancient protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,神秘之手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Hand of the Mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,只存在于神圣之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must be presented in a sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,-所以他选了这个房间  -神圣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's why he chose this room. - Sacred?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在礼物商店卖"我们人民"烈酒杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They sell "We the People" shot glasses in the gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是象征性的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:02.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个房间是为了纪念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This room was built as a tribute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,火灶神维斯塔神庙而建造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the Temple of Vesta in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的所作所为都有目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a purpose to-to everything he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有他所说的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And everything he's said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,"如其在上  如其在下"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"As above, so below."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:28.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是他挂电话前的最后一句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the last thing he said before he hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这  是罗马数字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There it is. Roman numerals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  根据减法计数法  这不是罗马数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. As a subtractive notation, it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-打扰一下  -可能是阿拉伯...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Uh, e-excuse me. - It could be, uh, an Arabic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:46.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不是阿拉伯语  -不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not Arabic. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我擅长阿拉伯语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a specialty of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:48.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能不能插一句话...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I can just interject for a quick second...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去像是如尼文的变种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it actually looks like a runic variation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:53.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,小天才们  拿反了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, smart people. It's upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以不是885  是SBB\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's not 885. It's S-B-B. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:00.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在国会大厦里面用这种计数系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We use that numbering system here in the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,地下二层  第13号房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Subbasement. Room 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  出发吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:41.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们来我父亲家干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing in my father's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:47.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}米克尔·阿达姆  中情局特工
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:47.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,中情局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:49.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,该你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的证件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me see some ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:53.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:04.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你跟我们去国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna need you to come with me to the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:14.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  拉里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Larry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:17.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,没想到  万能钥匙上没有万能这俩字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surprisingly, the master key doesn't say "master" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有标签  只有数字  赶紧找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No labels. Just numbers. Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:24.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  要下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Down we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:39.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You good, man? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:49.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在海平面以下  所以下面很潮湿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're below sea level, so it can get pretty wet down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:51.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,估计这也是没人愿意下来的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably why no one ever comes down anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:53.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,也没阻止彼得·所罗门下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't stop Peter Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:56.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们刚刚告诉我第13号房间是他的私人空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They just told me room 13 was designated as his private space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个钥匙孔比较奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, this keyhole's a bit funky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:01.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些钥匙都不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None of these are gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:09.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:11.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个壁烛台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This sconce.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:14.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,金合欢的枝条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sprigs of acacia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.23,0:24:19.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,共济会把它当做永生的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Masons consider it a symbol of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:02.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道彼得会在这下面做什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have any idea what Peter would have been doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:04.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.77,0:25:06.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,硫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sulfur.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.62,0:25:18.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许你没有自己想象的那么了解彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you don't know Peter as well as you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.73,0:25:41.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些像是人骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These bones look human.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.44,0:25:43.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,的确是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.94,0:25:49.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,这本书  使用人肉装订的还是怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this book, it's bound in human flesh or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.99,0:25:51.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是本圣经\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.40,0:25:53.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是什么祭坛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't some sacrificial altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.36,0:25:57.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是共济会的反思室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a Masonic Chamber of Reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.04,0:25:58.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,被用来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meant to be a place
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.79,0:26:02.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,反思自己的死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to come and reflect on one's own mortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.04,0:26:04.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,用别人的大腿骨来反思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With some dude's femur?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.83,0:26:07.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个比在四臂大象的前面吟唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That any stranger than chanting before a four-armed elephant
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.46,0:26:10.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者比在被钉在十字架的人脚下祈祷还奇怪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or praying at the feet of a man nailed to a cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.22,0:26:19.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -这个符号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Something wrong? - This symbol. The...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:21.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,利维坦十字架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Leviathan Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.89,0:26:25.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,不和谐  不应该摆在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's incongruous. It shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.06,0:26:26.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那这个呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.02,0:26:28.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,硫酸盐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Vitriol."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.15,0:26:30.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是缩写  你的拉丁文水平怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an acronym. How's your Latin?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.44,0:26:32.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,没阿拉伯语好  比德语强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not as good as my Arabic, better than my German.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.74,0:26:35.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,"入地心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Visita interiora terrae
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.70,0:26:39.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,净化后必会找到秘石"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rectificando invenies occultum lapidem."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.08,0:26:41.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,进入地心深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Visit the interior of the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:45.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,藉由矫正  你会发现黑色的石头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, purifying it, you will find a dark stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.21,0:26:47.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实是隐藏的石头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hidden stone, technically.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:51.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么意思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.92,0:26:53.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个共济会咒语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a Masonic mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.88,0:26:58.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,"净化它  你将找到隐藏的石头"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Purifying it, you will find the hidden stone."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.78,0:27:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把钥匙放回灯台了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you happen to put that key back in the sconce?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.79,0:27:23.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你指这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You-you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.58,0:27:25.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  没人告诉我放回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no one told me to put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:26.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许该快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.04,0:27:27.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,在炼金术中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In alchemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.96,0:27:31.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,第一次净化是溶解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the first purification is dissolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.42,0:27:34.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,表现为钙化物的溶解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}represented by the dissolving of calcifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.38,0:27:37.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些字是钙化物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These letters are calcifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.84,0:27:39.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是盐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.23,0:27:49.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,那堵墙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:51.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  这很令人惊叹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, it's remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.02,0:27:52.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  是那堵墙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.27,0:27:53.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想它在移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I think it's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.95,0:27:59.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些不仅仅是字符  它们是把手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These aren't just letters. They're handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.75,0:28:08.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,-该死的  我拿不出来  -好的  我们没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Damn it, I can't get it. - Yeah, yeah, we're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.42,0:28:10.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们没事  请快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're okay. Hurry, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.46,0:28:16.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.17,0:28:18.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个  那个撑不住了  我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not... That's not gonna hold. We got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.84,0:28:19.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,当心  当心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch out. Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:22.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快走  我们还在等什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry up. Come on! What we waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.71,0:28:53.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.13,0:29:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.22,0:29:03.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,兰登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.76,0:29:05.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,一步一步来  快来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One step at a time. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.68,0:29:07.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吗  快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you kidding me right now?! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.22,0:29:08.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,你已拿到这个了  快点  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got this. Come on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.73,0:29:10.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,向前迈一步  快点  继续向前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a step. Come on. Just keep going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.77,0:29:13.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,兰登  兰登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon! Langdon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.94,0:29:16.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,兰登  快点  振作起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon, come on! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.16,0:29:26.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.26,0:30:22.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我用了通用的共济会解密秘钥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used a common Masonic decryption key,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.92,0:30:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,所解出的明文  用专业术语说就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the, uh, resulting cleartext is, to use a technical term,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.18,0:30:28.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,胡言乱语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:30.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许你的解密方法不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe your decryption's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.14,0:30:32.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.18,0:30:34.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是个分段密码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's a segmented cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.77,0:30:38.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,当希腊人想储存秘密信息时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the Greeks wanted to store secret information,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.23,0:30:40.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们会把信息刻在一块石板上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they inscribed it on a tablet,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.86,0:30:42.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后把石板打成数块碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then shattered it into pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.86,0:30:45.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,每块碎片保存在不同的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}storing each piece in a separate location.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.03,0:30:46.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有集合所有碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only when the pieces were gathered together
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.49,0:30:48.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,才能正确解密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}could the secret be understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.99,0:30:50.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可以解释为什么缺失了顶部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which would explain why the top is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.91,0:30:52.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,尖顶石可以完善这段信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The capstone could complete the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.62,0:30:53.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,理论上如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.13,0:31:06.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你之前说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said before that, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.47,0:31:09.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许我没想象中那样了解彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe I didn't know Peter as well as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.81,0:31:13.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在为中情局工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was he working for the CIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.14,0:31:16.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.31,0:31:20.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.53,0:31:26.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-接吧  -像我们之前说过的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go. - Just like we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.45,0:31:28.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.74,0:31:30.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.88,0:31:31.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我  我会告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll... I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.58,0:31:33.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,但首先  我想知道彼得没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but first, I-I want to know that Peter's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.54,0:31:35.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要证明他还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want proof that he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.71,0:31:38.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, he's alive. But,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.17,0:31:40.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎么看  都在极度痛苦中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by any measure, in great distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.25,0:31:43.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我相信你说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You expect me to just accept that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.01,0:31:47.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你专注于你能控制的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect you to focus on what you can control,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.80,0:31:50.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,比如  他是生还是死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is whether he lives or dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.77,0:31:57.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了一个小的花岗岩金字塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a small granite pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.81,0:32:01.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,包括数值网格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Contains a numerical grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.98,0:32:03.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,但如果这是你的入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if this is your, portal,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.61,0:32:06.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我恐怕我有一些坏消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then I'm afraid I got some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.11,0:32:08.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这由我来判断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be the judge of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.78,0:32:13.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,破解网格需要进一步的背景信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any deciphering of the grid would require further context.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.66,0:32:14.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,尖顶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The capstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.04,0:32:21.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不会以为这么容易吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't think it was gonna be that easy, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.79,0:32:24.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有很多工作要做  罗伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have more work to do, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.80,0:32:26.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,把它找出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.67,0:32:29.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道从何开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I-I wouldn't know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.80,0:32:32.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.60,0:32:35.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且已经开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.06,0:32:40.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,找到了  离这4.8公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got the trace. Three miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.60,0:32:42.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,-快走  -我们马上赶去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go. - We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.19,0:32:44.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.69,0:32:46.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会在这袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna just sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.19,0:32:48.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是我们唯一的专家  我要你安然无恙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the only expert we have. I need you safe and secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:50.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,听起来像是不允许我离开的委婉说辞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like a nice way of saying I'm not allowed to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.95,0:32:51.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,是不允许\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.58,0:33:05.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有燕麦奶  豆奶可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, man. They didn't have oat. Soy okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.13,0:33:08.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行也得行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess it'll have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.78,0:33:29.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-谢了  -客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thanks. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.16,0:33:33.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.45,0:33:36.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you want to get out there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.16,0:33:37.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙找你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and help find your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.87,0:33:42.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我想中情局女警胜任有余\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I think CIA lady's pretty capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.13,0:33:46.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为她有事瞒着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think there's something she's not telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.47,0:33:53.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是个"知其所需"的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a "need to know" world, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.89,0:33:59.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在沙漠驻过两次军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did two tours in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.06,0:34:01.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还等着有人告诉我原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still waiting for someone to tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.65,0:34:05.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They like their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.45,0:34:14.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.95,0:34:20.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,这么多关于入口的传言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this talk about a portal,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.45,0:34:23.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得对我而言就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's what Peter was to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.92,0:34:25.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个门户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A gateway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.34,0:34:29.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,通往书籍和艺术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To books. To-to art.
