Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.07,0:35:33.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.74,0:35:35.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿杯酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get us a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.36,0:35:37.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,爸  威士忌吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad? Scotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.41,0:35:39.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  凯蒂  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good, Katie. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.95,0:35:46.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,感谢神灵  我有品位能介绍你们俩认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thank the gods I had the good taste to introduce you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.12,0:35:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳也许会说这是命运使然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine would probably call it fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:52.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是阿卡西场域中的永恒现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the immutable reality of the Akashic Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.34,0:35:55.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不相信这套说辞  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't believe in that kind of thing, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.55,0:35:56.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,老天  当然不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.72,0:35:58.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你却相信凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you do believe in Katherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.97,0:36:02.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你爱一个人  那最糟糕的事莫过于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The worst thing you can do if you love someone
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.01,0:36:05.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,让他们开始怀疑自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is to give them reason to doubt themselves.
