Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.86,0:36:13.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且也相信我们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and who trust in us
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.03,0:36:15.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论何种情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.78,0:36:19.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我从未拥有过那种人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I-I never had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.62,0:36:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在你有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.08,0:36:27.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  他从未放弃过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, he never gave up on me.
