Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.60,0:37:32.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,便让其受骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so let it be deceived."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.69,0:37:34.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,受骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.23,0:37:36.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  听上去像是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that sounds like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.77,0:37:38.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们倾巢出动却一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we brought everyone out here for nothing.
