Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:56.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里无事发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's all quiet over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.59,0:37:59.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we are secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.67,0:38:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.56,0:38:50.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you doing this?
