Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.20,0:39:53.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是没有兰登的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still no sign of Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.70,0:39:56.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,但已经派所有人去找了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we've got everyone looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.38,0:40:01.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想给你看点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to show you something.
