Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.18,0:40:11.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你问过我为什么对这案子这么在意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You asked about my interest in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.31,0:40:14.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,所罗门的孩子为我们工作过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Solomon's kid worked for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.85,0:40:17.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,很短暂  在安卡拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Briefly. In Ankara.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.85,0:40:21.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后他因为贩卖人口被关了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he got locked up for trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.99,0:40:27.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,三年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.90,0:40:29.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,监狱发生了暴动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there was a riot in the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.29,0:40:39.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,扎克里·所罗门被殴打致死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zachary Solomon was beaten to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.76,0:40:46.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  这之间有什么联系吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.88,0:40:49.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你要去土耳其寻找的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you're going to Turkey to find out.
