Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.87,0:41:15.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.91,0:41:18.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.25,0:41:19.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我并不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.96,0:41:21.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪  你...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going? What do...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.58,0:41:23.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  你...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.38,0:41:25.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是血吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.00,0:41:27.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.55,0:41:30.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.51,0:41:35.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,你必须相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.35,0:41:37.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要帮助你爸爸  我就得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'm gonna help your dad, I got-I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.27,0:41:38.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.78,0:41:41.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,抓走他的人想要我去找到一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The people who took him want me to find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.52,0:41:45.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,一件手工制品  一个古老拼图的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A... A-An artifact, a piece of a very old puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.69,0:41:47.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,-那我帮你  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Then I'll help you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.57,0:41:51.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们刚在那边杀了两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They shot two people back there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.57,0:41:53.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,就为了让我单独行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I could do this thing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.70,0:41:56.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不安全  我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's... It's not safe. I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.41,0:41:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.20,0:42:01.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,-凯瑟琳  -也许能有所帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Katherine. - Maybe it can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.38,0:42:05.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.75,0:42:08.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  但我爸说它的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, but Dad said that its secrecy
