Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.51,0:42:20.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,他这么说的吗  原话就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said that? Those exact words?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.56,0:42:21.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.56,0:42:26.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,他让我保证如果他有个三长两短的话就毁掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He made me promise to destroy it if anything ever happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.53,0:42:34.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟你一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.05,0:42:53.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.88,0:42:55.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,利维坦十字架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Leviathan Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.60,0:43:00.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,情况有变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's been a shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.43,0:43:03.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,空气中出现了异样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A stirring in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.90,0:43:07.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能感觉到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.78,0:43:16.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的命运现在掌握在罗伯特的手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your fate is in Robert's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.49,0:43:20.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,人类的命运也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the fate of mankind, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.55,0:43:35.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,但愿他不会令人失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, hopefully, he's not a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.01,0:43:39.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,像你儿子一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.22,0:43:44.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,可怜  令人失望的扎克里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor, disappointing Zachary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.85,0:43:48.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不了解我儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know nothing of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.60,0:43:49.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,可我了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.44,0:43:55.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我陪他走完了最后一程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was there with him in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.70,0:44:06.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我了结了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was the one who ended him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.31,0:44:27.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,兰登  我这是给你机会自己出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon, I'm giving you a chance to come out on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.27,0:44:28.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就派人去抓你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or I'm sending someone else in after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.60,0:44:30.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.27,0:44:32.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你挂了中情局的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you just hung up on the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.41,0:44:34.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\an5\pos(191.4,222.8)\fscy50\fscx50\fad(460,0)\bord0\fs28\b0\c&H84C3D9\3a&HFF\t(0,300,1,\blur0\fscx100\fscy100)}丹·布朗\N《失落的秘符》\N{\c&HE0DDD2}本季前瞻
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.48,0:44:36.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和彼得做了30年的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been friends with Peter for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.65,0:44:39.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他带我进入了这个组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was the one who brought me into the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.61,0:44:41.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,利维坦社的成立是基于一个信念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Leviathan Group was formed based on
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.45,0:44:45.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,即古老的智慧解锁了隐藏的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a belief that the ancient wisdom unlocked hidden power.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.45,0:44:48.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个力量落入坏人手中会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what would happen if this power fell into the wrong hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.62,0:44:51.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得彼得会为了保护那个秘密而牺牲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you think Peter would die to keep that secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.08,0:44:53.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.75,0:44:56.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,要是还有其他选择我们也不会来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't be here if had any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.05,0:44:58.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,关于佐藤你说对了  她有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were right about Sato. There's something she's hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.30,0:44:59.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,做你最擅长的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do what you do best.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.93,0:45:04.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,救回彼得的唯一方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only way to get Peter back
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.47,0:45:07.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是找到尖顶石  满足迈拉克的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is to find the capstone, give Mal'akh what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.68,0:45:09.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,时间不多了  我们必须完成这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time is running out. We have to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.64,0:45:10.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,不然我爸就没命了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or my dad is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.44,0:45:12.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,死亡对他来说是一种福气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Death will be a blessing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.98,0:45:18.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在进入我的世界了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in my world now.